{"tid":1709043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［藍扮黃可恥！］筲箕灣東大街「糖品」","createTime":"2019-11-11T20:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T15:50:29.000Z","uid":101045,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f61ee4479b93af400555095715268b7df1b89f","tid":1709043,"uid":101045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T20:56:28.000Z","msg":"藍到發黑但呃鳩我地入咗黃色經濟圈，事源個老細叫做葉少波Paul Yip。由於我認識此人，但並非有仇，只係我唔想佢扮可憐呃我地黃色經濟圈嘅人，佢前日先啱啱開始咗連儂場，牆上得幾張memo 紙。<br />\n佢個人言論非常有問題，第一，佢曾經喺自己個Wechat朋友圈度發表咗話我地有太多自己，所以導致香港咁亂，搞亂晒成個社會， 話我地係暴徒！！<br />\n第二，佢10月1日寫張紙仔喺門口話係「國殤日」，休息一日，佢扮完一日，之後個啲罷工一啲都唔理，佢仲返咗大陸做野！佢鋪頭曾經有休息幾日，但其實係佢內部員工有內訌，所以無人開工先被逼休息！請幫幫手到各Facebook page 或黃藍餐廳嘅App廣傳<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好再幫襯佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />假架！"},{"pid":"9a67460e7b14b7776009fb330d38d4a8df304ceb","tid":1709043,"uid":101045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T20:58:32.000Z","msg":"推推推！"},{"pid":"ca5dcfaa9dc0d83c4497648325478f3e6f04d912","tid":1709043,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T22:41:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"975bfa8e65dbae14a91686eac51ea8e562e07426","tid":1709043,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T22:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4b2995a566b5dc8a9041bea8cc7df7d1d68ad51","tid":1709043,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T23:00:24.000Z","msg":"假黃衰過藍"},{"pid":"3f6f7b5484438b5265182fc8795326b7086fada2","tid":1709043,"uid":163865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T23:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce59388e29aa72e85e9b4b4332528a0787caeb7e","tid":1709043,"uid":203889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re